{"tid":1126394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿小學時被揶揄「廢紙」　返母校用鈔票摑老師臉　23歲男自簽守行為","createTime":"2019-04-26T10:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T11:15:02.000Z","uid":220779,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e5c04112876f6491d15dddd01e98a6ea1a9ec24e","tid":1126394,"uid":220779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:58:10.000Z","msg":"23歲男子稱讀小學時不滿被老師比喻為「回收箱入面嘅藍廢紙」，一直耿耿於懷，去年重返母校外斥責該老師，更兩度用鈔票摑打對方臉孔。男生今在西九龍裁判法院承認一項「襲擊致造成身體傷害罪」，被判以自簽2000元守行為1年，並賠償事主1000元、支付300元訟費。<br />\n<br />\n報稱任金融經紀的被告莊洋洋（23歲）今承認，去年9月20日在葵涌慈幼葉漢小學外襲擊李家偉，對對方造成身體傷害。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官聽畢案情後曾問被告，為何用鈔票拍打別人臉部。被告回應稱，「佢（案中事主）比喻我係回收箱入面嘅藍廢紙」。裁判官聞言表示，一個人是否受人尊重，不是視乎掙多少錢，又形容被告「咁樣做好侮辱」。<br />\n<br />\n案情指出，被告讀小學時，曾因學業不佳被事主懲罰，令他耿耿於懷。至去年9月，被告在母校外情緒激動斥責事主，並用胸口撞撃事主3次，更從銀包取出11張港元和人民幣鈔票，兩度用鈔票摑打事主臉孔。被告又用手兩度抓住事主的衣領，導致對方頸部輕微擦傷。<br />\n<br />\n事主其他同事見狀報警，被告在警誡下表示「我只係同佢嘈，我冇打過佢」，到其後在錄影會面時指出，自己小學時因學業不佳遭事主懲罰，故透過撞撃及用鈔票摑打對方，來表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190426/s00001/1556274696090/不滿小學時被揶揄「廢紙」-返母校用鈔票摑老師臉-23歲男自簽守行為\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190426%2Fs00001%2F1556274696090%2F%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E6%99%82%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%B6%E6%8F%84%E3%80%8C%E5%BB%A2%E7%B4%99%E3%80%8D-%E8%BF%94%E6%AF%8D%E6%A0%A1%E7%94%A8%E9%88%94%E7%A5%A8%E6%91%91%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E8%87%89-23%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E8%87%AA%E7%B0%BD%E5%AE%88%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3Tjvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=fb85b0a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190426%2Fs00001%2F1556274696090%2F%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E6%99%82%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%B6%E6%8F%84%E3%80%8C%E5%BB%A2%E7%B4%99%E3%80%8D-%E8%BF%94%E6%AF%8D%E6%A0%A1%E7%94%A8%E9%88%94%E7%A5%A8%E6%91%91%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E8%87%89-23%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E8%87%AA%E7%B0%BD%E5%AE%88%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA&h=977780b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190426/s00001/1556274696090/不滿小學時被揶揄「廢紙」-返母校用鈔票摑老師臉-23歲男自簽守行為</a>"},{"pid":"a03cf3253ef1f5b152af7a414aac328d2e256c99","tid":1126394,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:59:13.000Z","msg":"記足十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5794c3660b2945254c7d7b14ca71cb5b1edea4","tid":1126394,"uid":177734,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:00:05.000Z","msg":"kai子報仇<br />\n十年未晚"},{"pid":"581a72cee7de07c875c7d43f1b5961fd5c169603","tid":1126394,"uid":78330,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:00:11.000Z","msg":"佢做咗好多人想做既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊間小學"},{"pid":"656fc53d451cbb559eae5ca9c7b9d78fd67dc998","tid":1126394,"uid":154127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf77c079b7b61d3770a0f940276668ac4e2c75b","tid":1126394,"uid":470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"581a72cee7de07c875c7d43f1b5961fd5c169603","tid":1126394,"uid":78330,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:00:11.000Z","msg":"佢做咗好多人想做既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊間小學"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:00:54.000Z","msg":"盲？"},{"pid":"8b65de56a6db2834d61ecad7bee8750a5133c601","tid":1126394,"uid":193893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:01:25.000Z","msg":"金融經紀+大疊銀紙=倫敦金???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0bd282a45c0ca7607f78b49ad4c92841fceaa85","tid":1126394,"uid":86337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04